headline: What New Catalysts Are Shaping the Narrative for O'Reilly Automotive Stock Now
summary: O'Reilly Automotive's fair value estimate has inched up to about $110.20 from $110.00, even as the discount rate has ticked higher to roughly 8.67% from 8.49%, reflecting a nuanced reassessment of both opportunity and risk after the latest pullback. This subtle recalibration ties back to analysts' growing conviction in the company's pricing power, resilient demand, and strengthening supply chain, which together support slightly stronger long term growth expectations despite a more demanding...
